'''''The African Who Wanted to Fly'''''  ( French   ) ni filime yo muri Gabon ya 2016 iyobowe na [[Samantha Biffot]]<ref>https://vimeo.com/ondemand/theafricanwhowantedtofly</ref> . Igice gishingiye kubuzima bwa Luc Bendza . Filime yakozwe mu ndimi ebyiri, [[Gishinwa|Igishinwa]] [[Igifaransa|n'Igifaransa]], kandi yari ifite insanganyamatsiko [[Icyongereza|y'icyongereza.]]<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/the-african-who-wanted-to-fly/</ref> 

== Umusaruro ==
'''''The African Who Wanted to Fly''''' yakozwe na Neon Rouge, afatanije na Theatre Company Theatre ( [[Ubufaransa]] )<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/event/the-african-who-wanted-to-fly/</ref>.  Scenese yafatiwe amashusho muri [[Gabon]], no mu Bushinwa. Umuziki wari ugizwe nindirimbo zishinwa.<ref>https://www.africa-in-motion.org.uk/2021-festival/programme/event/678/</ref> 

== Umugambi ==
Urebye filime Big Boss, umwana wo muri [[Gabon]] yavumbuye Kung Fu ahitamo kujya mu [[Ubushinwa|Bushinwa]] afite imyaka 15 gusa<ref>https://www.filmafrica.org/film-africa-events/the-african-who-wanted-to-fly-lafricain-qui-voulait-voler/</ref>. Yize ko azaba umunyafrica wambere wize ibihangano bya Kung Fu. Ahinduka inararibonye muri yo<ref>https://bampfa.org/event/african-who-wanted-fly</ref>.

== Kwerekanwa ==

* Iyi filime yarebwaga mu iserukiramuco rya sinema nyafurika muri kaminuza ya Duke ku ya 27 Gashyantare 2019<ref>https://canneseries.com/en/online/samantha-biffot-creator-of-the-series-mami-wata/</ref>. 
* ''Ku ya 19 Gicurasi 2017, Maysles Documentary Centre'' yerekanye filime mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya 24 rya New York muri New York<ref>https://www.nga.gov/research/casva/publications/center-report/center-41/members-reports/samantha-a-noel.html</ref>.

